---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://www.presciaiq.com.au" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Insights", "item": "https://www.presciaiq.com.au/insights" }
  ]
}
</script>
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "CollectionPage",
  "name": "PresciaIQ Insights",
  "description": "Expert insights on predictive analytics, AI for construction, marketing spend forecasting, and operational intelligence for Australian businesses.",
  "url": "https://www.presciaiq.com.au/insights",
  "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "PresciaIQ", "url": "https://www.presciaiq.com.au" }
}
</script>

<Layout title="Insights | Predictive Analytics &amp; AI Intelligence | PresciaIQ" description="Expert insights on predictive analytics, AI for construction, marketing spend forecasting, and operational intelligence for Australian businesses.">
  <div class="pt-32 pb-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div class="mb-16 text-center">
        <p class="text-primary font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-4 font-sans">Insights &amp; Intelligence</p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">The PresciaIQ Blog</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground font-sans max-w-2xl mx-auto">Deep dives into AI, predictive analytics, and the technology shaping Australian business.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Foundation Series Section -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-2">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">Foundation Series</span>
          <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-border"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-sans mb-8">The complete argument for predictive intelligence as an operating discipline. Four issues, designed to be read in order.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-4">
          <a href="/insights/the-reaction-tax" class="glass-card-hover p-6 flex flex-col group border-primary/20" style="text-decoration:none;">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">Issue 01</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground font-sans">8 min read</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-base font-bold text-foreground mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-snug">The Reaction Tax</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-sans mb-4 flex-1 leading-relaxed">Why most Australian businesses are paying to be surprised — and the hidden cost that never appears on a P&amp;L.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm font-bold text-foreground group-hover:text-primary transition-colors mt-auto font-sans">Read &rarr;</div>
          </a>
          <a href="/insights/where-the-reaction-tax-hides" class="glass-card-hover p-6 flex flex-col group border-primary/20" style="text-decoration:none;">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">Issue 02</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground font-sans">9 min read</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-base font-bold text-foreground mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-snug">Where the Reaction Tax Hides</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-sans mb-4 flex-1 leading-relaxed">A self-audit for the six places it shows up most — marketing, sales, projects, operations, customer health, and cash flow.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm font-bold text-foreground group-hover:text-primary transition-colors mt-auto font-sans">Read &rarr;</div>
          </a>
          <a href="/insights/three-tests-for-predictive-intelligence" class="glass-card-hover p-6 flex flex-col group border-primary/20" style="text-decoration:none;">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">Issue 03</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground font-sans">8 min read</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-base font-bold text-foreground mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-snug">The Three Tests for Predictive Intelligence</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-sans mb-4 flex-1 leading-relaxed">How to tell real predictive tools from dashboards in costume — before you spend a dollar on any of them.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm font-bold text-foreground group-hover:text-primary transition-colors mt-auto font-sans">Read &rarr;</div>
          </a>
          <a href="/insights/the-action-gap" class="glass-card-hover p-6 flex flex-col group border-primary/20" style="text-decoration:none;">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">Issue 04</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground font-sans">9 min read</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-base font-bold text-foreground mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-snug">The Action Gap</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-sans mb-4 flex-1 leading-relaxed">Why most predictive deployments fail, and the four conditions that fix them. The model worked. The org did not.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm font-bold text-foreground group-hover:text-primary transition-colors mt-auto font-sans">Read &rarr;</div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- All Articles Section -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-2">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">All Articles</span>
        <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-border"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-sans mb-8">Practical intelligence on AI, predictive analytics, and the decisions that determine whether Australian businesses grow or stall.</p>
