          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-snug">Why Every Australian Marketing Team Needs a ROAS Prediction Tool</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-sans mb-4 flex-1 leading-relaxed">How ROAS prediction tools are helping Australian marketing teams forecast campaign returns before spend is committed.</p>
