            <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground font-sans">5 min read</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-snug">What is an Operational Intelligence Platform?</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-sans mb-4 flex-1 leading-relaxed">Understand what an operational intelligence platform does, how it differs from traditional BI, and whether your Australian SMB would benefit from one.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm font-bold text-foreground group-hover:text-primary transition-colors mt-auto font-sans">Read Article &rarr;</div>
